title: CryptoMiner.rar
description:
Windows x64 Cryptocurrency miner, for nVidia GPU's

Let your PC make you money! This easy-to-use miner will let you mine a number of very profitable cryptocurrencies. Bitcoin and ethereum mining is now out of reach for most home users. Large organizations have whole warehouses of specialised mining equipment which makes it impossible to earn even a dollar a day mining these cryptos.

Fortunately, this miner allows you to mine Electroneum, Monero, and other cryptocurrencies that use the Cryptonight algorithm, which is designed to be resistant to this expensive hardware, making it profitable for your average home user who wants to make money using only their home computers GPU or CPU.

This specific miner is for nVidia cards only.

Note: Some anti-viruses may give a false positive on crypto miners. This is a well-known fact that can be easily confimed by googling online. This miner is virus FREE. I've checked it myself, and its the miner I personally use
